	]em
	" features many returning characters from 
	[em 
		"Dream Land 2
	]em
	". 
	[em 
		(__wikiLink|displaytext=Kirby 64: The Crystal Shards|href=/974G)
	]em
	" serves as the sequel to this game. 
	$LF
]div
[div class=p 
	"After the events of 
	[em 
		(__wikiLink|displaytext=Kirby's Dream Land 2|href=/1660G)
	]em
	", Kirby and Gooey are on a fishing trip, when all of a sudden, Dark Matter appears and shatters the planet's rings. He then proceeds to possess various Dream-Landers, including King Dedede. Kirby and Gooey team up with Rick, Coo, and Kine, as well as new characters Pitch, ChuChu, and Nago, in order to stop Dark Matter.
	$LF
